        "layout": "text-bottom-center"
      },
      {
        "text": "A low temperature will make A.I. stay close to what you started with. ",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/8a7978d2f7ee428b65717debb24f58fc-music-panels-10-2-b.gif",
        "key": "music_ai_panels_aibeatblock_temperature_3-4a5ea7cb-f73e-4ee8-9cf0-7c6681166f71",
        "layout": "text-bottom-center"
      },
      {
        "text": "A high temperature will make A.I. generate more surprising sounds.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/b8bcf8ce4a930b29f639befa6b6e6032-music-panels-10-3-b.gif",
        "key": "music_ai_panels_aibeatblock-d2ba442b-68e2-47f1-abd5-15c49f5d243c",
        "layout": "text-bottom-center"
      },
      {
        "text": "Try different temperatures and see what happens!",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/8a88710511104a1214316c42094ed92e-AI Temp Panel_4.jpeg",
        "key": "music_ai_panels_aibeatblock_temperature_1-10253ec1-46f6-4286-a421-f54b336a2489",
